trans-unit.source: Defines a common set of properties for the several display modes that a Web Parts page can enter.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et vanlig sett med egenskaper for flere Vis-modus som en webdeler-side kan skrive inn.

trans-unit.source: A Web Parts page can enter several different display modes.
trans-unit.target: En webdeler-side kan skrive inn flere forskjellige visningsmodus.

trans-unit.source: In each display mode, certain elements of the Web Parts user interface (UI) are either hidden or displayed, and certain kinds of user modifications to a page are either enabled or disabled.
trans-unit.target: I hver visningsmodus enkelte elementer i webdeler-brukergrensesnittet (UI) enten er skjult eller vises, og enkelte typer brukerendringer på en side er aktivert eller deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control contains the implementation for the display modes that are available in the Web Parts control set, and manages the display modes for a page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll inneholder implementeringen for Vis moduler som er tilgjengelige i webdeler kontrollen settet og administrerer visningsmodi for en side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists fields that represent the available display modes.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser felt som representerer de tilgjengelige Visningsmodiene.

trans-unit.source: |Display mode|Description| |------------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>|Displays Web Parts controls and UI elements in the normal mode in which end users view a page.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode>|Displays zone UI elements and enables users to drag Web Parts controls to change the layout of a page.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>|Displays special editing UI elements and enables end users to edit the controls on a page.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>|Displays special catalog UI elements and enables end users to add and remove page controls.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode>|Displays special connections UI elements and enables end users to connect Web Parts controls.|
trans-unit.target: | Visningsmodus | Beskrivelse | |------------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>| Viser webdeler kontroller og UI-elementene i normal modus som sluttbrukere ser på en side. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode>| Viser sone UI-elementene, og gjør det mulig for brukere å dra webdeler kontroller for å endre oppsettet for en side. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>| Viser spesielle redigering UI-elementene, og gjør det mulig for sluttbrukerne mulighet til å redigere kontroller på en side. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>| Viser spesielle katalogen UI-elementene, og gjør det mulig for sluttbrukerne mulighet til å legge til og fjerne sidekontrollene. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode>| Viser bestemte tilkoblinger UI-elementene, og gjør det mulig for sluttbrukerne mulighet til å koble webdeler kontroller. |</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a value for the name of the display mode.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en verdi for navnet på visningsmodus.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object is never created because the class is abstract.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekt er ikke opprettet fordi klassen er abstrakt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: At run time, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> class as the base class to create objects for each of the various page display modes.
trans-unit.target: Under kjøring av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollere bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>klasse som basisklassen til å opprette objekter for hver av de ulike side viser modiene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The name of the display mode.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på visningsmodus.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that determines whether users can change the layout of a Web Parts page when the page is in a certain display mode.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som bestemmer om brukere kan endre oppsettet for en webdeler side når siden er i en bestemt visningsmodus.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if users can change the page layout; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis brukere kan endre oppsettet siden. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether a certain display mode is associated with a class that derives from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om en bestemt visningsmodus er knyttet til en klasse som er avledet fra den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When a Web Parts page enters a display mode whose AssociatedWithToolZone property is set to `true`, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control interprets that to mean that an associated class derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone> class, and that additional user interface (UI) elements need to be displayed.
trans-unit.target: Når en webdeler side går inn i en visningsmodus der AssociatedWithToolZone-egenskapen er satt til `true`, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen tolker som å bety at den tilknyttede klassen er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone>klassen, og at flere elementer i brukergrensesnittet (UI) skal vises.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: For example, when a page enters edit mode, special zones that contain UI elements for editing Web Parts controls appear on the page.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når en side går inn i redigeringsmodus, vises spesielle soner som inneholder UI-elementene for redigere webdeler kontroller på siden.

trans-unit.source: This behavior is made possible because the AssociatedWithToolZone property value on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode> field is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjøres mulig fordi egenskapen AssociatedWithToolZone verdi i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>feltet er satt til `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the display mode is associated with a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone"></xref> class; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis visningsmodus er knyttet til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone"> </xref> klasse; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om brukere kan tilpasse en side mens siden er i en bestemt visningsmodus.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control instance on the current page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> kontroll-forekomsten på gjeldende side.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis brukere kan tilpasse en side. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
